data.description: Discover your mountain dream home, where stunning panoramic views of the majestic mountains greet you from every corner. This spacious retreat offers an open floor plan with high ceilings, creating an atmosphere of grandeur bathed in natural light. Enormous windows frame the mountains like living works of art, and a deck off the master bedroom offers a serene escape. Entertain, dine, or simply soak in the natural beauty on the expansive deck. With a $1200 carpet allowance, you can infuse your personal style into this already impressive home, which comes complete with all newer appliances and a new roof. Don't miss your chance to experience the perfect blend of luxury and mountain living – schedule a showing today! $10,000 SELLER PAID CLOSING COSTS/RATE BUY DOWN!!!!
